= The 7th Saga (SNES) - SRAM Map =

This page documents the save RAM (SRAM) layout for The 7th Saga.

==Overview==

The 7th Saga uses 8 KB of battery-backed SRAM at $70:0000-$70:1fff for saving game progress. The save system uses XOR checksums and mirrors save slots for data integrity.

