! Property !! Value
|-
| SRAM Size || 8 KB ($2000 bytes)
|-
| Save Slots || 3 (mirrored twice)
|-
| Slot Size || $500 bytes
|-
| Checksum || 16-bit XOR
|-
| Bank Address || $70:0000-$70:1fff
|}

==Memory Layout==

There are 3 save slots of $500 bytes each, which are mirrored in a second set of 3 slots for redundancy.

Default for $0002-$10ff is $ff. Default for $1100-$1fff is $00. Unused areas generally follow this pattern.

